## What This Module Does

This module provides the real-time WebSocket communication layer between the VJLive3 core DMX engine (P2-D1) and the web-based UI. It handles transmitting DMX state changes to the UI, receiving manual overrides from the UI, and managing "DMX Learn" mode. In "Learn" mode, the system listens for incoming DMX signals and maps them to specific UI parameters, storing these relationships in a `ParameterMapping` system.

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- It does NOT transmit Art-Net or sACN packets over the network directly (that belongs to P2-D2).
- It does NOT define the core DMX engine or fixture profiles (that belongs to P2-D1).
- It does NOT handle audio-reactivity (that belongs to P1-A3 / P2-D5).

